  "notes": "DSM-Firmenich is a global leader in nutrition, health, and beauty ingredients formed by the merger of DSM and Firmenich. Their Pentavitin Postbiotic is a breakthrough postbiotic carbohydrate complex derived from plant fermentation that provides exceptional 72-hour deep hydration while supporting skin microbiome health. The ingredient strengthens the skin barrier and provides anti-inflammatory benefits, making it ideal for sensitive skin formulations. With extensive clinical research backing its efficacy and COSMOS certification options, Pentavitin Postbiotic is perfect for brands seeking science-backed, clean beauty ingredients."
